  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个关于零售订单管理系统和GitHub资产关联的心智图，核心是Retail_OrderManagement这个根节点。它下面应该分两大块：一个是系统本身的domains结构，另一个是跟人员相关的PersonOfInterest。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root(Retail_OrderManagement)",
        "domains",
        "PersonOfInterest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，domains下面需要细化吗？比如subdomains这种层级结构？另外PersonOfInterest这边，我理解为是追踪关键人员的信息，需要包含哪些具体维度？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subdomains",
        "nested subdomains",
        "emails",
        "repos",
        "companies",
        "social accounts",
        "phone numbers",
        "org memberships",
        "Credentials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，domains下面要有subdomains，再往下是nested subdomains三级嵌套。PersonOfInterest这边需要全面一点：emails、repos、companies、social accounts、phone numbers、org memberships，还有Credentials。另外domains里除了结构，还要补上EmailAddress和apps这两个实际业务元素。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmailAddress",
        "apps",
        "Credentials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，domains分支和PersonOfInterest分支都加上了。现在GitHub相关的部分怎么安排？是挂在PersonOfInterest下面还是独立出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitHubOrg",
        "GitHubRepo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GitHub部分要独立成两个节点：GitHubOrg和GitHubRepo，都是跟root平级的。GitHubOrg下面有Repositories、commits、members；GitHubRepo下面要有Committers、branches、forks，还有Credentials。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repositories",
        "commits",
        "members",
        "Committers",
        "branches",
        "forks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：GitHubOrg和GitHubRepo是分开的两个一级分支，不是从属关系。GitHubRepo的Credentials和PersonOfInterest的Credentials是同名但不同上下文对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Credentials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对的，同名但语境不同。最后还需要一个Service节点，也是一级分支。Service下面挂Credential，Credential再展开四层：username、token、key、secret。这样整个凭证管理的层次就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service",
        "Credential",
        "username",
        "token",
        "key",
        "secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
